data.revised_prompt: Imagine an adorable dog partaking in a joyous dance within the confines of a lush forest. Money, designed with the dog's face, whimsically floats down from the sky, creating a peculiar shower of wealth. Instead of using the conventional anime style, the art style of the image should resemble colorful and exaggerated illustrations prevalent during the late 19th century. To capture the surrealness of the scene, please have the text 'DOGGIE COIN TO THE MOOOON' prominently featured in the image.
